
         
         <p>As part of the current development target of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">denote</code>, users can
access the commands we provide via a convenient <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">menu-bar-mode</code> entry.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>commit 818c6ae08b32c33893f2bbbc3152e3b64be289c5
